title: Tiger Mask Wrestling Vids!
description:
Back after a long long time.

  My son got me back into wrestling after a long period, and I have really latched on to the mask wrestlers.  Tiger mask is one of them!

Here are a bunch of matches, and even a 2 part documentary about the first Tiger Mask.

The quality is about a 6 or 7 on the a/v as they are webrips or ripped from youtube.

enjoy and please please seed, sharing is caring.

PS: look out for my next uploads which will be Ultimo Dragon and Mistico!
